name: 千雪
text:
レクタングラー型、マミー型……？
色々あるんだ……
trans:
Rectangular-style, mummy-style...?
There's a lot of different types...

name: 甜花
text: うちにあるのは……どの形……？
trans: Which type... is the one at home...?

name: 甘奈
text:
んー……
このレクタングラー型……だったかな……？
trans:
Hmm... 
It's probably this rectangular-style one... I think...?

name: 千雪
trans:
......?
You have a sleeping bag at home?

name: 甘奈
text:
あ、ううん！
うちにあるのは子どもの時の
trans:
Ah, not exactly!
The one at home is from when we were kids.

name: 甘奈
text:
昔、家族でキャンプした時のだから
もう使えないかな
trans:
We had it from when our family went camping a long
time ago. I don't think we can use it now.

name: 甜花
text:
なーちゃん、キャンプ道具に、
双眼鏡とか……なかったっけ……？
trans:
Naa-chan, in our camping goods,
were there any binoculars...? Do you remember...?

name: 甘奈
text:
あ……そうだ
あったら、使えるかも
trans:
Ah... That's right.
If there are, we could use them.

name: 甜花
text:
（シュラフ、準備オッケー
双眼鏡も、オッケー……）

name: 甜花
text:
（甜花の帽子と……
なーちゃんのマフラー……）

name: 甜花
text:
（カードゲームなら、
３人でできるかな……？）
trans:
(We should all be able to play...
so long as it's a card game, right......?)

name: 甜花
text:
甜花、
うるさかったかな……
trans:
Was Tenka...
a little too loud......?

name: 甘奈
text:
ううん、何か飲もうって思っただけだから
大丈夫だよ
trans:
Not at all, I just wanted to get a little something to
drink. Don't worry.

name: 甜花
text:
にへへ……
明日、流星群って思ったら、わくわくして……
trans:
Nihehe......
The meteor shower tomorrow... is exciting......

name: 甘奈
text:
そっかぁ
えへへ、甘奈も楽しみ
trans:
I see.
Ehehe, I'm looking forward to it too.

name: 甜花
text:
ね……！
お星さま、なーちゃんと、千雪さんと……！
trans:
Right......?!
Seeing the stars... with Naa-chan... and Chiyuki-san...!

name: 甜花
text:
カードゲームだったら、
星、見ながらできるかな……？
trans:
Could we... play a card game...
while we look at the stars......?

name: 甜花
text:
あ……
やっぱ、なんでもない……
trans:
Oh......
Actually, don't worry about it......

name: 甜花
trans:
...Are you tired, Naa-chan?
You should sleep......

name: 甜花
text: 風邪、治ったばっかだし……
trans: You've only just recovered from your cold......

name: 甘奈
text:
それは、どっちかというと
甜花ちゃんの方だからね？
trans:
I'd be willing to wager that you're feeling a bit more
tired than me, right?

name: 甜花
text:
あ、ほんとだ……
にへへ……

name: 甜花
text:
じゃあ……
甜花もお部屋、戻る……
trans:
In that case.....
Tenka... will go back to her room......

name: 甜花
text:
眠れるか……
わかんないけど……
trans:
She doesn't know......
if she'll be able to sleep though......

name: 甘奈
text:
目を閉じてじっとしてるだけでも、
体は休まるみたいだよ
trans:
Even if you just close your eyes and lie there without
moving, it's basically the same thing.

name: 甜花
text:
じゃあ甜花、
じっとしてる……！

name: 甘奈
text:
うんっ
それで、明日に備えよ～
trans:
Yeah,
and then, you can do more preparations tomorrow～

name: ママ
text: ほらほら、みんな。願い事は？
trans: Come on, everyone. What are your wishes?
